  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Study of genetic polymorphisms of CYP #A and MDR-1 genes in Thai HIV-1 infected patients on
      saquinavir/ritonavir.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      Genetic polymorphisms will be investigated by polymerase-chain reaction (PCR) and drug levels
      of saquinavir will be determined by high phase liquid chromatography with UV-detected (HPLC).
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
